<Article
  title="What FAIR Plan Really Covers in California"
  description="What California's FAIR Plan covers, what it doesn't, what changed in 2024, and whether it can pay claims after the January 2025 LA fires."
  pillar="residual-markets"
  lastUpdated="June 2026"
